videos.description: Brad Nessler and Sean Farnham break down how another big game from Ben Simmons was the catalyst for LSU in getting the win over Georgia.
videos.headline: Simmons' big game key to LSU's win

videos.description: LSU coach Johnny Jones isn't happy with how his team struggled down the stretch against Georgia, but he is happy to get the win and is looking ahead to facing No. 1 Oklahoma.
videos.headline: Jones: Team didn't finish strong, but got the win
